      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW IKE (5) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish third last time, beaten 2 lengths (34.83) behind Warm Cockles at this track. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Sure to be about the mark. URANA PARALLAX (4) stalked the lead after a clean break from the tricky draw and went on to finish second (34.63) at Sandown in a Grade 4/5 over 595m. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Can feature again. NIGEL DEVERE (8) missed the frame two back but wound up strongly last time, finishing on late when third (27.83) in a Special conditions race at Bendigo. Has a good record here including two wins. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Expected to feature again. MEPUNGA SHADOW (1) is worth consideration.",
